#eNCA anchor Masego Rahlaga is in conversation with ANC spokeperson Pule Mabe. Mabe is unpacking the party's NEC decisions. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The ANC’s National Executive committee says it’s accepted that the party is on a downward spiral. The party has put together a renewal plan for the year ahead and says without renewing and rebuilding the organisation it will fail at its mission. READ: ANC KZN leadership race hots up From 20-23 January, the party held its planning meetings virtually. eNCA anchor Masego Rahlaga spoke to ANC spokesperson Pule Mabe in the video above.